"{\"uid\": \"express.co.uk-sport-othersport-1932269-2024-Paris-Olympics-gymnastics-high-bar\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  BBCviewers have called for investigation following a dramatic men's high bar final that saw a number of gymnasts fall.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 120, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In what proved a bizarre competition, only two athletes managed to avoid coming off the bar, with Japan's Shinnosuke Oka winning gold.\", \"from\": 121, \"to\": 255, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 219, \"end\": 224, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\", \"score\": 0.9999778250085779, \"rank\": 1.8823281273873146e-05, \"text\": \"Japan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\"}, {\"begin\": 227, \"end\": 241, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shinnosuke_Oka\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Shinnosuke Oka\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shinnosuke_Oka\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shinnosuke_Oka\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Colombia's Angel Barajas took silver, while Zhang Boheng of China overcame a stumble to take bronze.\", \"from\": 257, \"to\": 357, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 257, \"end\": 265, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Colombia_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.5878910500909154, \"rank\": 0.6971489743320868, \"text\": \"Colombia\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Colombia_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Colombia_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 274, \"end\": 281, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rod_Barajas\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 4.796312726326167e-13, \"text\": \"Barajas\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rod_Barajas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rod_Barajas\"}, {\"begin\": 301, \"end\": 313, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zhang_Boheng\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Zhang Boheng\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zhang_Boheng\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zhang_Boheng\"}, {\"begin\": 317, \"end\": 322, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.6062218486276953, \"rank\": 0.6492995562434037, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Oka's winning score of 14.533 would only have been enough for third place in Tokyo three years ago, and during the final, fans were left questioning the apparatus used.\", \"from\": 359, \"to\": 527, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 436, \"end\": 441, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9999999876040421, \"rank\": 7.722681057942688e-09, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"@DrMeowMeowJr wrote on X: \\\"They need to investigate something is going on with that high bar because there is no way people are falling.\\\"\", \"from\": 529, \"to\": 666, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"@bctoniii added: \\\"There is surely something off with the equipment on the high bar.\", \"from\": 667, \"to\": 750, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Why is this not being enquired?\\\"\", \"from\": 751, \"to\": 783, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"@Pinklilycat echoed similar sentiments, writing: \\\"I think the equipment needs checking.\", \"from\": 785, \"to\": 872, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This men's high bar has been a disaster.\\\"\", \"from\": 873, \"to\": 914, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"@LoLoByke went a step further, posting:\\\"We need to investigate these bars.\", \"from\": 915, \"to\": 989, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"First the beam for the women and now the high bar for the men?\\\"\", \"from\": 990, \"to\": 1053, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The reference to the women followed similar chaos in the beam final on Monday morning.Simone Biles was one of a number of gymnasts to slipduring her routine, scuppering her hopes of a fourth gold medal in Paris.\", \"from\": 1055, \"to\": 1266, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1260, \"end\": 1265, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999987826413, \"rank\": 1.2174270932865655e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Discovery+is the new home of the Olympics.\", \"from\": 1270, \"to\": 1312, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The streamer is set to broadcast 3,800 hours of sport live from Paris.\", \"from\": 1313, \"to\": 1383, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1377, \"end\": 1382, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999987826413, \"rank\": 1.2174270932865655e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sports fans can getDiscovery+ for \\u00a33.99a month until the end of 2024 via Amazon Prime's video channels.\", \"from\": 1385, \"to\": 1488, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1458, \"end\": 1470, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazon_Prime\", \"score\": 0.9490751179424906, \"rank\": 0.05365737762870464, \"text\": \"Amazon Prime\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazon_Prime\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazon_Prime\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This also comes with anAmazon Prime 30-day free trial.\", \"from\": 1489, \"to\": 1543, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"On BBC, Beth Tweddle suggested that gymnasts would have been making alterations to their planned routines as they watched the chaos unfold.\", \"from\": 1545, \"to\": 1684, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1548, \"end\": 1551, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\", \"score\": 0.9881204009027231, \"rank\": 0.011768701055123586, \"text\": \"BBC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\"}, {\"begin\": 1553, \"end\": 1565, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beth_Tweddle\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Beth Tweddle\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beth_Tweddle\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beth_Tweddle\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But fellow pundit Christine Still was at a loss when trying to explain the errors.\", \"from\": 1685, \"to\": 1767, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"When you are up first you have got to go all out with the difficulty,\\\" said Tweddle.\", \"from\": 1769, \"to\": 1854, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But if you are getting towards the end of the field of play, and you are seeing scores are quite low, actually gymnasts drop their difficulty.\\\"\", \"from\": 1855, \"to\": 1999, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She added: \\\"It's maybe the tension of the wires of the bar, if they are a little bit tight it can cause falls.\", \"from\": 2001, \"to\": 2111, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But the gymnasts have had plenty of time to warm up and the coaches have tension gauges to see what the tension is.\", \"from\": 2112, \"to\": 2227, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's very unusual and bizarre.\\\"\", \"from\": 2228, \"to\": 2259, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We use your sign-up to provide content in ways you have consented to and to improve our understanding of you.\", \"from\": 2261, \"to\": 2370, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This may include adverts from us and 3rd parties based on our understanding.\", \"from\": 2371, \"to\": 2447, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can unsubscribe at any time.\", \"from\": 2448, \"to\": 2480, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy Policy  The high number of falls meant the final lasted longer than envisaged, as officials scrambled to clean up afterwards.\", \"from\": 2481, \"to\": 2622, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And it meant frustration for Biles and co. with the start of the women's final delayed as a result.\", \"from\": 2623, \"to\": 2722, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Not that Oka was complaining.\", \"from\": 2724, \"to\": 2753, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2733, \"end\": 2736, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oka_Crisis\", \"score\": 0.9999999191659331, \"rank\": 8.08339885527674e-08, \"text\": \"Oka\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oka_Crisis\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oka_Crisis\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Having already helped Japan win gold in the team final, and taken the individual all-around title, he followed up bronze on the parallel bars earlier this morning with a fourth medal in Paris.\", \"from\": 2754, \"to\": 2946, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2776, \"end\": 2781, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\", \"score\": 0.9999778250085779, \"rank\": 1.8823281273873146e-05, \"text\": \"Japan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\"}, {\"begin\": 2940, \"end\": 2945, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999987826413, \"rank\": 1.2174270932865655e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"SEARCH  CONNECT WITH US  TODAY'S PAPER  See today's front and back pages, download the 